====Entering the room====
* '''Sir Tinley:''' Ah, [player name], you have arrived. Speak to me to begin your task.
* {{tact|end}}

====Talking to Sir Tinley====
* '''Sir Tinley:''' Ah, welcome [player name]. I have but one clue for you to pass this room's puzzle: 'Patience'.
* {{tact|end}}

